&lt;h1 id=""&gt;&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;h2 id="overview"&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;This project was an immersive pop-up located on Grand Street in SoHo, inspired by manga-media cult classics Akira + Attack on Titan.&lt;/p&gt;
