&lt;em&gt;Kodansha House immersive pop-up&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="project-description"&gt;Project Description&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;Our team was asked to create 2 timeline-based video booths replicating moments from the Kodansha-produced anime classics.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Fantastic Flora</title><link>https://traversable-dale.github.io/projects/fantastic-flora/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://traversable-dale.github.io/projects/fantastic-flora/</guid><description>&lt;table&gt;
