&lt;h1 id=""&gt;&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;h2 id="overview"&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;This project was an immersive installation made for the very last edition of &lt;a href="https://ra.co/promoters/80563" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Shaker Mountain&lt;/a&gt; - a &amp;lsquo;smart house and techno in a family-and-friends setting on 250 acres of tree-topped mountain land&amp;rsquo; [Resident Advisor]&lt;/p&gt;
