&lt;em&gt;Fantastic Flora suspended installation&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="project-description"&gt;Project Description&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;I was involved in technical direction, integration, and installation of this project, working directly with designer + lead fabricator &lt;a href="https://www.behance.net/shreyapatel119" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Shreya Patel.&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>The Blue Paradox</title><link>https://traversable-dale.github.io/projects/blue-paradox/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Mar 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://traversable-dale.github.io/projects/blue-paradox/</guid><description>&lt;table&gt;
