&lt;h2 id="overview"&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;The Blue Paradox is an immersive exhibition at the &lt;a href="https://www.griffinmsi.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Griffin Museum of Science and Industry&lt;/a&gt; in Chicago, IL.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Much of what&amp;rsquo;s publicly available can be found on the &lt;a href="https://www.msichicago.org/explore/whats-here/exhibits/blue-paradox" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;museum&amp;rsquo;s page&lt;/a&gt; which provides a window into the experience.&lt;/p&gt;
