&lt;h1 id=""&gt;&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;h2 id="overview"&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;Camata is &amp;ldquo;a self-directed film operated by a learning machine, a manifestation of an inhuman entity enacted upon by a set of robotic operators, performing a final rite of passage on a human skeleton found unburied in the Atacama Desert.&amp;rdquo; - Marian Goodman Gallery&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Yo-Yo Ma - Spiegel im Spiegel</title><link>https://traversable-dale.github.io/projects/yo-yo/</link><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jan 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://traversable-dale.github.io/projects/yo-yo/</guid><description>&lt;table&gt;
